description: AE Raspberry Lowfat Yogurt Made in Iowa and hours fresh when it arrives on stores shelves.  Crafted in small batches, and made with premium fruits and flavorings, and colored with fruit and vegetable juice rather than artificial colors. The smooth, pudding-like texture is a trademark of AE Yogurts because the dairy takes time to make each flavor. The yogurt is made with 4 probiotics providing a total of 200 billon probiotics in each serving. Vitamin D is added to make it healthier and helps with the absorption of the Calcium. Gluten Free
title: Anderson Erickson Raspberry Lowfat Yogurt - 6oz
